ons to blockers or identifying and executing on partnership needs. Additionally, as Coinbase continues to embrace decentralization, you’ll help lead our strategy on supporting DAOs and ensuring Coinbase is a leader and valued partner in key decentralized ecosystems.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
