&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A BA/BS degree or equivalent practical experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience working in a B2B sales type role in Technology and/or Finance, preferably with a global and/or enterprise customer base&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
